high_descs: Go to the sidetable in front of the couch which is on your left.
Pick up the empty mug off of the table.
Turn and go to the microwave to the right of the couch if you are facing the couch.
Put the mug in the microwave, turn the microwave on and take the mug out after it finishes.
Turn around and go back to the sidetable in front of the sofa.
Put the mug back on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Microwave a mug and put it on the SideTable.

high_descs: Walk forward to the couch and then turn left towards the sidetable.
Pick up the mug near the back of the top of the coffee table.
Turn around and walk towards the shelves, then turn left at the shelves to go to the microwave.

Open the microwave door, put the mug in the microwave, close the microwave door, turn on the microwave for a few seconds, open the microwave door, take the mug out of the microwave, and close the microwave door.
Turn to the left and walk to the sidetable.
Set the mug back onto the sidetable, this time to the very left towards the front, below the pen.
anns.task_desc: Heat the mug in the microwave and return it to the SideTable.

high_descs: pick up the mug from the table.
walk over to the microwave and put the cup inside the microwave.
Start the microwave to heat up the coffee in the mug.
Open the microwave door and get the coffee cup out of the sidetable.
Take the mug back to the sidetable and place it down.
anns.task_desc: re-heating the liquid in the mug on the side table.
